ÿÜCommands
---------------------------------------------------------------

aim.refresh.icon     : requests user's icon
aim.remove.me        : removes you from someone's buddy list
aim.warn.user        : warns someone
aim.font.crash       : crashes 4.8 users and below
aim.smiley.lag	     : sends a shitload of new smileys (6 ims)
aim.exp;X;X;X;	     : sets your sidebar, im background, and icon
			example: aim.exp;evil;evil;redrose;
aim.game.crash	     : crashes people
aim.null.crash       : crashes aims with add-ins enabled
aim.vis.true	     : appear online
       .false	     : appear offline
       .flutter	     : toggle flutter timer
aim.gen.response     : "forges" a response from someone
aim.script.*	     : executes script "*" on current user
aim.bot.add          : adds a screen name to the bot list
       .rem          : removes a screen name from the bot list

Suffixes
---------------------------------------------------------------

.noco                : ignores any commands on im
.away                : set your away message as current im
.ar                  : changes current im to auto response
.lim		     : for large ims, splits them up into 2500 byte
			pieces
.htmlon              : changes less than and greater than html
			codes to actual <'s and >'s

Replacements
---------------------------------------------------------------

*nl*                 : "new line" for chat room text
*0n*                 : "null" character for anything
